\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Div\_Index distribution per model and method ($n\!=\!50$, bs-pairs $1\!\leftrightarrow \!8$ and $8\!\leftrightarrow \!32$, log $x$ axis). BF16 shows a left tail (early divergence) especially on DeepSeek-7B and Llama-8B; \textsc  {DetermLLM}\xspace  shifts the distribution right, raising the median by $29$--$43\%$ on the GQA models. Format follows Yuan et al.\nobreakspace  {}\citep  {yuan2025numerical}.\relax }}{7}{figure.caption.4}\protected@file@percent }
